---
title: Brown  Sugar-Glazed Pork Tenderloin with Sweet Potato Wedges and Brussels Sprout-Apple Hash
description: A mixture of brown sugar and spices creates a beautiful glaze on juicy pork tenderloin. Apples, cranberries, and Brussels sprouts are the perfect combination in this sweet and savoury hash. You’ll be shocked by how easily this impressive dinner comes together!
